 Former President Olusegun Obasanjo, Governor Ibikunle Amosun of Ogun State, Former Secretary-General, Emeka Anyaoku, and other dignitaries stormed the 75th birthday celebration of the paramount ruler of Egbaland, Dr. Adedotun Aremu Gbadebo on Friday 14th September, 2018. The birthday ceremony began on Monday with a press conference, followed by a visit to the less-privilege homes and later with special prayers led by Muslim and Christian Clerics. Thereafter, reception took place at the Olusegun Obasanjo Presidential Library which was attended by Obasanjo and other dignitaries. Details coming. 